summary:

The major technologies I use are Ruby, Rails, HTML5, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery, Ajax, JSON, AWS(EB, RDS, S3, EC2), Sinatra, API's, OAuth, BCrypt, Devise, Handlebars, SQL, and more.
